{"tid":49592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[絲打請進]m到好痛點搞","createTime":"2016-12-21T22:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T06:35:20.000Z","uid":42197,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10da2d147e902e6b90676130f09d171509a0fc38","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T22:55:29.000Z","msg":"十月開始有食避孕藥，食咗兩個月到，之後十二月中去咗旅行，計過撞正m到所以食多咗幾日藥去延經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知一停食就出事，m到前一日就開始痛，痛到依加第三日都仲係好好好好好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依加係痛到行路都要曲住個身<br />\n明明以前都唔會痛得咁誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點先可以唔痛啊啊啊啊啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/065527_1aa2af8fa216d1c71fd0da67936078df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F065527_1aa2af8fa216d1c71fd0da67936078df.jpg&h=2334b11b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b4300cd8cc8d3b307c35fb50cec9a75b83f0b0e7","tid":49592,"uid":57622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T22:57:10.000Z","msg":"飲薑茶<br />\n食必理痛<br />\n如果仲係好痛，建議睇醫生"},{"pid":"2aa468a91eaea4482152726ca63187cd64aeda4d","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲薑茶<br />\n食必理痛<br />\n如果仲係好痛，建議睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我尋日開始到依加已經食咗五粒panadol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真心痛到肚餓都唔想起身"},{"pid":"020b65d82c07348304390a2bc4e4e0aeecd0cf97","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:03:43.000Z","msg":"屌點解咁都有負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4e8cafa12fc3143f59a8c5ac1f7cf48ad6bc34","tid":49592,"uid":57388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:04:47.000Z","msg":"冇得搞嫁喎<br />\n唯有食藥 必理痛係最好 <br />\n不過食得多會冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 試過痛到暈撚咗喺街<br />\n琴晚半夜第一次痛到醒咗<br />\n<br />\n伸唔直條腰是常識吧<br />\n<br />\nI know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924fbbaaba6c841ab1a8806e23e45a27643468f2","tid":49592,"uid":58622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:06:21.000Z","msg":"飲熱水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a84a46e2f6e19cb607cece90be22e80e9ba107","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇得搞嫁喎<br />\n唯有食藥 必理痛係最好 <br />\n不過食得多會冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 試過痛到暈撚咗喺街<br />\n琴晚半夜第一次痛到醒咗<br />\n<br />\n伸唔直條腰是常識吧<br />\n<br />\nI know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依加係feel到個肚餓到咕咕聲之餘仲要好撚痛<br />\n啱啱俾出面啲雀嘈醒 食完panadol都仲痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係想繼續瞓姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8073e747a3a3c7759d7b5add793a7a47e6f6a0b","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:08:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲熱水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我連床都唔想落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a67087d7ad0734e7405a99d9172aff548d47b6","tid":49592,"uid":68546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:11:47.000Z","msg":"日本隻止痛藥有用過必利痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有狂飲薑茶 同埋特濃既熱朱古力"},{"pid":"76a7d523a0325bbbccc71bd87969c9c2fb6cacb0","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:18:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本隻止痛藥有用過必利痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有狂飲薑茶 同埋特濃既熱朱古力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港有無得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0849864d3312321ffe8673f38e082d2ec691b20","tid":49592,"uid":58622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲熱水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我連床都唔想落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啊啊啊啊"},{"pid":"9fc2b30be5810b83520d1dcf1aa5e0a74b048a72","tid":49592,"uid":17520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:23:03.000Z","msg":"狂食必利痛經痛配方<br />\n利申當糖食食足3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f6034aa10433f3656dadb0a2ddc8c591af35b0","tid":49592,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:23:54.000Z","msg":"去藥房買 ibuprofen ，200mg一粒，理論上2粒夠做，你好唔掂可以3粒<br />\n止痛好過食必理痛，反正你唔洗消炎"},{"pid":"090de8b5f5f5ff6ea7194f06408c3ea9adb9b539","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狂食必利痛經痛配方<br />\n利申當糖食食足3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一日食幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我啲m會嚟成七日 啲m巾點慳都會用晒要再買 好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78495d71beafb1af905c35d23eb45f1ed88d715a","tid":49592,"uid":21744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:25:35.000Z","msg":"唔好再食藥了，狂敷熱水袋，狂瞓覺，飲熱柚子蜜"},{"pid":"2040dfcb1f491fd13e53ae5a6d5c82671775aa60","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去藥房買 ibuprofen ，200mg一粒，理論上2粒夠做，你好唔掂可以3粒<br />\n止痛好過食必理痛，反正你唔洗消炎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪就咁講藥名就得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e21c7f305dd05771642dc0a6b1e8c8e8c23947","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好再食藥了，狂敷熱水袋，狂瞓覺，飲熱柚子蜜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n避孕藥就諗住停一個月睇下點，panadol就真係無辦法，一痛就好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd419cc7005efa2db061194a0e5ac4ddc6567ab1","tid":49592,"uid":17520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>狂食必利痛經痛配方<br />\n利申當糖食食足3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一日食幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我啲m會嚟成七日 啲m巾點慳都會用晒要再買 好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早午晚 每次2粒<br />\n認真mode 我試曬所有方法得食藥先救到我<br />\n痛到出冷汗就要入醫院打止痛針<br />\n咩薑茶咩熱朱古力咩暖水袋咩訓教<br />\n全部都係多舊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa62aa5100db9f5f1084192e43e15ac754743d6f","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>狂食必利痛經痛配方<br />\n利申當糖食食足3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一日食幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我啲m會嚟成七日 啲m巾點慳都會用晒要再買 好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早午晚 每次2粒<br />\n認真mode 我試曬所有方法得食藥先救到我<br />\n痛到出冷汗就要入醫院打止痛針<br />\n咩薑茶咩熱朱古力咩暖水袋咩訓教<br />\n全部都係多舊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一日無咁痛果陣沖熱水涼都仲好少少<br />\n點知到尋晚第二日 沖涼沖到彎住腰都係痛<br />\n薑茶就仲未試過不過尋晚食咗碗老薑蕃薯湯圓糖水 都係好好好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b4f24ca20ded78511245e1d2f65349418be14d","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一日食幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我啲m會嚟成七日 啲m巾點慳都會用晒要再買 好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早午晚 每次2粒<br />\n認真mode 我試曬所有方法得食藥先救到我<br />\n痛到出冷汗就要入醫院打止痛針<br />\n咩薑茶咩熱朱古力咩暖水袋咩訓教<br />\n全部都係多舊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一日無咁痛果陣沖熱水涼都仲好少少<br />\n點知到尋晚第二日 沖涼沖到彎住腰都係痛<br />\n薑茶就仲未試過不過尋晚食咗碗老薑蕃薯湯圓糖水 都係好好好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺床係跪住扒低瞓就好似好少少 但無理由咁樣就瞓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f25acae321dc023c5f4f74b221243f4c7b3b67c","tid":49592,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:33:00.000Z","msg":"試下撳下穴位<br />\n內腳眼果度<br />\n用三隻手指度位 最尾果隻手指位大大力撳落去 <br />\n利申：聽中醫師鳩up"},{"pid":"c9aa982eda5c15a678172ef380954fa819050ac0","tid":49592,"uid":17520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一日食幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我啲m會嚟成七日 啲m巾點慳都會用晒要再買 好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早午晚 每次2粒<br />\n認真mode 我試曬所有方法得食藥先救到我<br />\n痛到出冷汗就要入醫院打止痛針<br />\n咩薑茶咩熱朱古力咩暖水袋咩訓教<br />\n全部都係多舊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一日無咁痛果陣沖熱水涼都仲好少少<br />\n點知到尋晚第二日 沖涼沖到彎住腰都係痛<br />\n薑茶就仲未試過不過尋晚食咗碗老薑蕃薯湯圓糖水 都係好好好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常就唔關避孕藥事既 可能係你食多左凍野？今個月<br />\n如果關藥事你隻藥都唔應該再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842b5cd9e696459ab436b01b11ba526a9592d188","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早午晚 每次2粒<br />\n認真mode 我試曬所有方法得食藥先救到我<br />\n痛到出冷汗就要入醫院打止痛針<br />\n咩薑茶咩熱朱古力咩暖水袋咩訓教<br />\n全部都係多舊魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我第一日無咁痛果陣沖熱水涼都仲好少少<br />\n點知到尋晚第二日 沖涼沖到彎住腰都係痛<br />\n薑茶就仲未試過不過尋晚食咗碗老薑蕃薯湯圓糖水 都係好好好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常就唔關避孕藥事既 可能係你食多左凍野？今個月<br />\n如果關藥事你隻藥都唔應該再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能去旅行食得多甜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇埋下次嚟m點 如果停食會好啲就唔再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b23613f1fe61cc62036d6c94ddf069e0926a06","tid":49592,"uid":42197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下撳下穴位<br />\n內腳眼果度<br />\n用三隻手指度位 最尾果隻手指位大大力撳落去 <br />\n利申：聽中醫師鳩up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/073705_e805d9657059b5383c858eecca2d9121.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F073705_e805d9657059b5383c858eecca2d9121.jpg&h=c8f72aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個？"},{"pid":"df066926ce309ec6dcc0e80366d7f3e2b598c766","tid":49592,"uid":11774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T23:40:05.000Z","msg":"我本身就係會有到仆街嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽人講 飲八珍湯可以斷尾 以後唔痛<br />\n飲過一次 難飲到仆街<br />\n其次係食必利痛隻經痛配方<br />\n都OK嘅 一時時啦<br />\n最近係由佢痛幾粒鐘 痛完佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我次次都痛 都唔知做乜撚<br />\n有次喺屋企痛到無咗意識<br />\n暈咗好耐先醒返 好似瞓咗場覺咁"}]}